section.para:
If is enabled, the alternate IP must be either:
an IP from an existing UDP SIP listener configured in Marina.Rodeo, but one that is different from all the other UPD listeners;
an IP that is different from the UDP SIP listeners configured in Marina.Rodeo.

If is enabled, the alternate port must be either:
a port from an existing UDP SIP listener configured in Marina.Rodeo, but one that is different from all the other UPD listeners;
a port that is different from the UDP SIP listeners configured in Marina.Rodeo.
